Class CassandraHandlerJDBC

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sb.db.cassandra.CassandraHandlerJDBC

  • public class CassandraHandlerJDBC
extends Object
    This class is used if a jdbc driver is involved. The dbproperties class is mandatory for the constructor of this class Requires: cassandra-jdbc-1.2.5.jar and cassandra-jdbc-dependencies
